sbourne) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>韦斯特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanyes-twitter-and-instagram-accounts-locked-after-antisemitic-posts-3325446">于 2022 年 10 月首次被指控反犹太主义，</a>此前他在 Twitter 和 Instagram 上发布了一系列帖子，导致他在这两个社交媒体网站上的账户被暂停。</p><p>在最初提出反犹太主义指控后，这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-antisemitic-comments-dropped-lawyer-talent-agency-3334864">被他的律师、经纪公司</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-is-reportedly-no-longer-signed-to-def-jam-3335238">唱片公司</a>解雇，而包括巴黎世家 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/balenciaga-cuts-ties-with-kanye-west-over-antisemitic-comments-3333697">Balenciaga</a> ) 和阿迪达斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adidas-ends-kanye-west-deal-in-light-of-rappers-anti-semitic-comments-3335494">Adidas)</a>在内的多个时尚品牌也终止了与他的合作关系。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-backlash-3325627">世界各地的名人和政治家谴责他的言论</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-says-he-doesnt-believe-in-the-term-anti-semitism-its-not-factual-3330802">韦斯特在接受新闻国家队的克里斯·科莫采访时表示，他不“相信”反犹太主义一词</a>。</p><p>他最近就自己的反犹太言论<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-apologises-jewish-community-antisemitic-comments-3563267">向犹太社区道歉</a>。</p><p> 12 月 26 日，韦斯特分享了一篇用希伯来语写的帖子。该消息被翻译成英文，内容如下：“对于我的言论或行为造成的任何意外爆发，我真诚地向犹太社区道歉。我无意伤害或不尊重，我对我可能造成的任何痛苦深表遗憾。</p><p> “我致力于从自己做起，从这次经历中学习，以确保未来有更大的敏感性和理解力。您的原谅对我来说很重要，我致力于弥补并促进更大的团结。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系 West 的代表征求意见。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 抨击“反犹太分子”坎耶·韦斯特 (Kanye West) 未经许可使用“战猪”样本的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看 Blink-182 首次现场演唱《One More Time》歌曲，拉开 10 年来首次澳大利亚巡演的序幕https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-blink-182-give-one-more-time-songs-their-live-debut-as-they-kick-off-first-australian-tour- 10年-3585224？utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-blink-182-再给一次歌曲-他们的现场首次亮相，因为他们开始了第一次澳大利亚巡演- 10年内Elizabeth AubreyFri, 09 Feb 2024 21:16:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3585224 <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blink-182 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队本周在珀斯开始了澳大利亚巡演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-blink-182-give-one-more-time-songs-their-live-debut-as-they-kick-off-first-australian-tour-in-10-years-3585224">Watch Blink-182 为“One More Time”歌曲带来了现场首秀，开启了 10 年来的首次澳大利亚巡演，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1269" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blink-182 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Blink-182-Photo-by-Christopher-Polk_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>昨晚（2 月 8 日）以“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">One More Time</a> ”歌曲首次现场亮相，开启了十年来的首次澳大利亚巡演。查看下面演出中的镜头和粉丝反应。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">Blink-182 –“再来一次”评论：一次令人惊讶的感人重聚</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队在珀斯的 RAC Arena 演出，这是他们自 2013 年参加声波音乐节以来首次在澳大利亚演出。在那场演出中，乐队由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hoppus">Mark Hoppus</a> 、 <a href="/artists/tom-delonge">Tom Delonge</a>和鼓手 Brooks Wackerman 组成。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-barker">特拉维斯·巴克（Travis Barker）</a>由于害怕飞行而错过了那次巡演。自从乐队与 Barker 一起出现在那里已经有 20 年了。</p><p>乐队今晚（2 月 9 日）在珀斯举行另一场演出，然后在阿德莱德、墨尔本、悉尼、布里斯班、墨尔本举行演出。随后他们将前往新西兰在奥克兰和基督城演出。查看完整的日期列表并<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/blink-182-australia-tour-2024-dates-cities-tickets-3455167#:~:text=Blink%2D182%20have%20announced%20a,for%20their%202024%20Australia%20tour.&amp;text=Today%2C%20concert%20organiser%20Live%20Nation,at%20the%20Rod%20Laver%20Arena.">在此处</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p>除了演奏《The Rock Show》、《Feeling This》和《I Miss You》等经典热门歌曲外，乐队还首次推出了 2023 年专辑《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/blink-182-one-more-time-review-lyrics-tracklist-3517188">One More Time</a> 》中的歌曲。</p><p>乐队首次现场演奏了《Fuck Face》和《Turpentine》，并首次完整演奏了《Anthem Part 3》。</p><p>查看演出的镜头和反应以及下面的完整列表： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3ED5r0hrk1/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886